26#include "objc-private/common.h"
27#include "objc/NXConstStr.h"
28
29@implementation NXConstantString
30
31-(const char *) cString
32{
33 return (c_string);
34} /* -cString */
35
36-(unsigned int) length
37{
38 return (len);
39} /* -length */
40
41@end
